					&lt;p&gt;Generally you won't find coriander or other spices added to hefeweizen beers, due to the traditional &lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reinheitsgebot"&gt;beer purity law&lt;/a&gt;.  However, one famous exception is Gose: &lt;a href="http://www.germanbeerguide.co.uk/gose.html"&gt;http://www.germanbeerguide.co.uk/gose.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

				</Text>
